content: FWangZil: Fixed a critical parameter parsing issue in plugin-evm TransferAction (PR #965, +77k/-48k lines) while working on Solana liquid staking support with two open PRs (#1435, #1461). Created and closed three issues, including a bug report for parameter handling (#1439) and a feature request for Solana liquid staking (#1434). Contributed sporadically across 5 days this month, with a balanced focus between bug fixes (43%) and new features (29%), modifying 46 files with +3369/-861 lines of code.
